headline: ARK Invest Snaps Up $23.5M in BitMine and Bullish Shares Across Flagship ETFs
summary: The purchases, disclosed in recent trade filings, consisted of 387,000 shares of BitMine and 144,000 shares of Bullish, with ARK Innovation ETF (ARKK) leading the way.
